title: Dana Kellin Diamond Black Spinel Necklace
description:
An ancient gemstone worn in royal courts from Beijing to Rome, Black Spinel is said to offer the fortunate wearer protection while evoking empowerment and inspiration. The soothing, healing rare stones are wrapped in 14 karat gold wire and paired with pave diamonds in an impressive geometric pendant. Dana Kellin jewelry is best known for its intricate, meticulous wire-wrapping details.

  • Dimensions: Necklace 16.25 in, pendant .4 in
  • Materials: 14K gold wire and chain, black spinel gemstones, diamond pave
